        <p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: "Source Sans Pro", sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; padding: 0px;'>Fatura Teslim: Fatura sipariş teslimatı sırasında teslimat adresine sipariş ile birlikte teslim edilecektir.</p>
